@startuml erd
title Schema — announcements table

!define TABLE(name) entity name << (T,#ffcc66) >>
hide methods
hide stereotypes

TABLE(announcements) {
  +id : INTEGER <<PK>>
  --
  message    : VARCHAR(5000)  NOT NULL
  author     : VARCHAR(255)   NOT NULL
  created_at : TIMESTAMPTZ    NOT NULL
  updated_at : TIMESTAMPTZ    NOT NULL
  deleted_at : TIMESTAMPTZ    NULL
  ..
  INDEX ix_announcements_deleted_at_id
        (deleted_at, id)
}

note bottom of announcements
  Soft delete: ``deleted_at IS NOT NULL``
  hides the row from default queries.
  Index supports the common
  "list non-deleted, paginated" query.
end note
@enduml
